te>個人認為倉頡作為輸入法極失敗，啲碼好唔intuitive <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家有智能電話，要學唔難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n速成二碼+選字--&gt;三鍵=有智能常用字記錄、只需記頭尾碼、方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n倉頡三碼/四碼--&gt;三、四鍵=多輸入一鍵，相對唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速成先唔方便啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三鍵&gt;四鍵，輸入速度差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速成要揀字 煩到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：速成用家</blockquote><br />\n所以更加要儘快學識倉頡、尤其係電腦呢啲必須輸入全碼嘅輸入法，唔識<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>真</del></span>打真係好麻煩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4bd8e5687be346fd99abf5c1711410d2e49b0471","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電話用倉頡, 電腦用速成<br />\niphone打頭幾個倉頡碼就會出到隻字, 好方便<br />\nwindow反而要打晒先出到, 雖然識但都係速成方便</blockquote><br />\n我電腦都係用倉頡，其實倉頡都有速成功能，就係頭尾碼中間打*"},{"pid":"97fb432745b28054bc34bcf11bde2a44b769a4f5","tid":222964,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個人認為倉頡作為輸入法極失敗，啲碼好唔intuitive <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家有智能電話，要學唔難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n速成二碼+選字--&gt;三鍵=有智能常用字記錄、只需記頭尾碼、方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n倉頡三碼/四碼--&gt;三、四鍵=多輸入一鍵，相對唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速成先唔方便啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三鍵&gt;四鍵，輸入速度差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速成要揀字 煩到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：速成用家</blockquote><br />\n所以更加要儘快學識倉頡、尤其係電腦呢啲必須輸入全碼嘅輸入法，唔識真打真係好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n有時打打下字個人呆咗變咗咩碼都唔記得 變咗打粒*代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIphone就方便啲 打個重字就ok"},{"pid":"f10b84a3242eb54679f169896fccd552791fbd24","tid":222964,"uid":96048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:36:32.000Z","msg":"理論上拼音係最快<br />\n因為拼音嘅聯想功能強過倉頡好多倍<br />\n點解？因為用嘅人多"},{"pid":"4b49a11750f248a724e0f881259cc87e3047b95e","tid":222964,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上拼音係最快<br />\n因為拼音嘅聯想功能強過倉頡好多倍<br />\n點解？因為用嘅人多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到最後都係靠反應速度、記位：速成最少碼<br />\n<br />\n結論：速成最方便"},{"pid":"2e642368f85aaa0e31ee1029bf53012cd0ece690","tid":222964,"uid":9366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"如果講快 縱橫輸入法應該會仲快<br />\n不過好少人用<br />\n<br />\n利申 速成"},{"pid":"db50b0b3ddc77c401cebdf7fa31f0616f8810f64","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上拼音係最快<br />\n因為拼音嘅聯想功能強過倉頡好多倍<br />\n點解？因為用嘅人多</blockquote><br />\n錯啦拼音先唔會快，因為有同音字問題，倉頡重碼率低好多"},{"pid":"2ecbd815b2e6512f01e56ebd8f31df42e00ac827","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28ea6f0c5ebb96ed3ec267dca7782ed652e4c4e","tid":222964,"uid":28549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"講快九方真係屈機<br />\n完全諗唔明<br />\n倉頡就通用d<br />\n速成只係比學唔識倉頡既人用<br />\n熟倉頡,唔駛諗碼既人一定唔會用速成<br />\n有時借人電腦用如果要用返咁上下時間都會偷偷地裝個倉頡, 還果時先del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家電話有埋常用字, 未打晒d碼已經搵到仲快左d<br />\n筆劃不予置評"},{"pid":"67a48da79418e4ab9997e90e1d5df5cf4acff5e9","tid":222964,"uid":96048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>理論上拼音係最快<br />\n因為拼音嘅聯想功能強過倉頡好多倍<br />\n點解？因為用嘅人多</blockquote><br />\n錯啦拼音先唔會快，因為有同音字問題，倉頡重碼率低好多</blockquote><br />\n錯喇<br />\n拼音唔會逐個字去打 通常係打詞語或句子嘅拼音<br />\n跟著會generate最接近嘅句子<br />\n同埋拼音可齋打聲母<br />\n姐係打 jt 會出 今天 呢啲咁嘅常用字<br />\n<br />\n利申：打開倉頡 學緊拼音"},{"pid":"5bba50098915a9e0b96dd9cd2a184881e072f89e","tid":222964,"uid":96048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>理論上拼音係最快<br />\n因為拼音嘅聯想功能強過倉頡好多倍<br />\n點解？因為用嘅人多</blockquote><br />\n錯啦拼音先唔會快，因為有同音字問題，倉頡重碼率低好多</blockquote><br />\n錯喇<br />\n拼音唔會逐個字去打 通常係打詞語或句子嘅拼音<br />\n跟著會generate最接近嘅句子<br />\n同埋拼音可齋打聲母<br />\n姐係打 jt 會出 今天 呢啲咁嘅常用字<br />\n<br />\n利申：打開倉頡 學緊拼音</blockquote><br />\n同埋估計香港嘅新一代會因為普教中 打多左拼音<br />\n速成倉頡會成為我地老一輩嘅產物"},{"pid":"f4516d10bfeb9df9f271b608c9f481f1b527e97f","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>理論上拼音係最快<br />\n因為拼音嘅聯想功能強過倉頡好多倍<br />\n點解？因為用嘅人多</blockquote><br />\n錯啦拼音先唔會快，因為有同音字問題，倉頡重碼率低好多</blockquote><br />\n錯喇<br />\n拼音唔會逐個字去打 通常係打詞語或句子嘅拼音<br />\n跟著會generate最接近嘅句子<br />\n同埋拼音可齋打聲母<br />\n姐係打 jt 會出 今天 呢啲咁嘅常用字<br />\n<br />\n利申：打開倉頡 學緊拼音</blockquote><br />\n同埋估計香港嘅新一代會因為普教中 打多左拼音<br />\n速成倉頡會成為我地老一輩嘅產物</blockquote><br />\n咁呢個叫快拼姐"},{"pid":"3ccca7f0f26c1a61f85625a66feb0127380801c2","tid":222964,"uid":102872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"屌講到科技發達 當然係通過直接講來打字最方便啦<br />\nIphone真係detect得唔錯 幾準下"},{"pid":"af81475a7feef55fb31356a84c76d57f1a8b9a97","tid":222964,"uid":84432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"手機用速成，電腦打字用倉頡<br />\n都係兩個月前先由速成轉用倉頡 因為本身打字比較慢而且速成又要搵個字係第幾個所以去學倉頡 到而加開始上手 真係番唔到轉頭 好爽"},{"pid":"8781661abb4d69bf409ba388c159a8d650fb038b","tid":222964,"uid":96048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4rqQq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4rqQq6.jpg&h=b0040abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拼音係聯想方面根本就有先天嘅優勢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢咁都估到我想打咩"},{"pid":"a704443f712428ef2d9ebfedc277e2d500fbffd9","tid":222964,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"倉頡用家到此一遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電話同電腦都係用倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea433428c1fbbaf9cc662f6235d016ccd189e9a","tid":222964,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4rqQq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4rqQq6.jpg&h=b0040abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拼音係聯想方面根本就有先天嘅優勢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢咁都估到我想打咩</blockquote><br />\n有殘體字嘅"},{"pid":"6b2acc00503930ab74109d34f708f3ae4f555b70","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到科技發達 當然係通過直接講來打字最方便啦<br />\nIphone真係detect得唔錯 幾準下</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦，iphone個直接講打字成日會錯意架，邊忽快？！"},{"pid":"9a79b83af76c1538d28d1f0ec607a0db31598c8b","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4rqQq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4rqQq6.jpg&h=b0040abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拼音係聯想方面根本就有先天嘅優勢<br />\n<br />\n佢咁都估到我想打咩</blockquote><br />\n打粵語得唔得先，如果淨係支援蝗語係無咩用"},{"pid":"29779dee64bba7a1004e1f0ce41db84d28500fc9","tid":222964,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"好後悔小學冇好好咁學<br />\n而家學緊倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77074b81aa95c83eb30e2d5b18f01e806c44c8ca","tid":222964,"uid":96048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4rqQq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4rqQq6.jpg&h=b0040abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拼音係聯想方面根本就有先天嘅優勢<br />\n<br />\n佢咁都估到我想打咩</blockquote><br />\n打粵語得唔得先，如果淨係支援蝗語係無咩用</blockquote><br />\n冇計 粵語拼音少人用<br />\n達唔到big data嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a231cbe2e80441bef04961e6fee17d06ed05d196","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好後悔小學冇好好咁學<br />\n而家學緊倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好講以前啦，以前想查個碼都煩到嘔，唔識寫隻字連個碼都查唔到，又要諗詞語組嚟查，諗唔到又係查唔到"},{"pid":"577f9e0446738b2040dabe91efbf838b28c411c4","tid":222964,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"都係既 但老老實實電話個keyboard細細地有時想打快d 好易會撳左隔籬粒英文字而打錯字 但筆劃得6個格所以無咁易打錯"},{"pid":"f5cd8f43c4d65d5a3a6f53974cf17ab6476bfcc1","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4rqQq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4rqQq6.jpg&h=b0040abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拼音係聯想方面根本就有先天嘅優勢<br />\n<br />\n佢咁都估到我想打咩</blockquote><br />\n打粵語得唔得先，如果淨係支援蝗語係無咩用</blockquote><br />\n冇計 粵語拼音少人用<br />\n達唔到big data嘅效果</blockquote><br />\n咁你講到再快都係無咩用，最終都係要用番倉頡，完"},{"pid":"384bee310829ff029c3545e62b664cc5e6b5d8a0","tid":222964,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"倉頡的確係快過速成好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe378a580bbe5f3def131aa6bfb89d3d25ff0914","tid":222964,"uid":19357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"岩呀 打左成十幾年倉頡"},{"pid":"ce22e34ab8874e7ff167cdd3f5845084b5d09413","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩呀 打左成十幾年倉頡</blockquote><br />\n其實十年前無智能電話唔記得隻字點打係點查碼架？"},{"pid":"fb821d559a75e8c7d8bb3d693cb5bad429296679","tid":222964,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82554f4d36dca89bdfbfc02edcb6004ea7ba1a83","tid":222964,"uid":43870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"語音輸入先至係王道<br />\n而家已經好撚準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4793bf59e1be15cbd876a582ffab424d95a5292","tid":222964,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:28:11.000Z","msg":"真男人 用倉頡"},{"pid":"3d5e0b281d85db8193deeb7b7e76327fc6394cc1","tid":222964,"uid":10931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"又黎倉頡優越論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要學拆字既輸入法本身已經係ON9"},{"pid":"c3d5a1506e49853cb8180fc6081e961b66cdeb3e","tid":222964,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n依家有智能電話，要學唔難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n速成二碼+選字--&gt;三鍵=有智能常用字記錄、只需記頭尾碼、方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n倉頡三碼/四碼--&gt;三、四鍵=多輸入一鍵，相對唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速成先唔方便啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三鍵&gt;四鍵，輸入速度差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速成要揀字 煩到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：速成用家</blockquote><br />\n所以更加要儘快學識倉頡、尤其係電腦呢啲必須輸入全碼嘅輸入法，唔識真打真係好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n有時打打下字個人呆咗變咗咩碼都唔記得 變咗打粒*代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIphone就方便啲 打個重字就ok</blockquote><br />\n電腦都係重呀<br />\nZ key 呀嘛"},{"pid":"42a347cd47ea8f584ef6afb95a7f9c88d6716ab1","tid":222964,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講快九方真係屈機<br />\n完全諗唔明<br />\n倉頡就通用d<br />\n速成只係比學唔識倉頡既人用<br />\n熟倉頡,唔駛諗碼既人一定唔會用速成<br />\n有時借人電腦用如果要用返咁上下時間都會偷偷地裝個倉頡, 還果時先del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家電話有埋常用字, 未打晒d碼已經搵到仲快左d<br />\n筆劃不予置評</blockquote><br />\n無錯！話速成快過倉頡嘅，根本本就係懶閪，無認真少少去練下倉頡。由速成過渡去倉頡，感覺根本就係兩個世界。倉頡快幾個level，速成只係輔助，好偶然唔識拆嘅冷門字先會用。"},{"pid":"734d3c2f4f370896aa32664c138a3b2e31bf40e5","tid":222964,"uid":113042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講快九方真係屈機<br />\n完全諗唔明<br />\n倉頡就通用d<br />\n速成只係比學唔識倉頡既人用<br />\n熟倉頡,唔駛諗碼既人一定唔會用速成<br />\n有時借人電腦用如果要用返咁上下時間都會偷偷地裝個倉頡, 還果時先del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家電話有埋常用字, 未打晒d碼已經搵到仲快左d<br />\n筆劃不予置評</blockquote><br />\n無錯！話速成快過倉頡嘅，根本本就係懶閪，無認真少少去練下倉頡。由速成過渡去倉頡，感覺根本就係兩個世界。倉頡快幾個level，速成只係輔助，好偶然唔識拆嘅冷門字先會用。</blockquote><br />\n認同，最初我都係用速成<br />\n後尾自練倉頡之後就返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a119864e9a0155c97860098fee2cf9cc6a8e2f09","tid":222964,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"358a689fb6b89602e4519cd123a68b11086886c8","tid":222964,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:37:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9375bdb44e90d32d6085c86c64b9ef1768a3f61b","tid":222964,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3638d94c90ada58fa553bf72db21951e6b43e6a1","tid":222964,"uid":69528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"熟習既話倉頡會快過速成好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345a2fd5fe7987b54b17cc52fe89592318017697","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2758b92bd65aaf6bec3425ed77da91ce22936ac1","tid":222964,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩呀 打左成十幾年倉頡</blockquote><br />\n其實十年前無智能電話唔記得隻字點打係點查碼架？</blockquote><br />\n打開本倉頡書慢慢查，如是者打耐咗，一個月左右就冇乜問題。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 用咗倉頡十幾年"},{"pid":"2b09d47671b2df79579b29c9e0f2eee126166e4e","tid":222964,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40e3f7174ce306aff1ea1478bffe7cb83e835158","tid":222964,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前速成<br />\n轉左倉頡之後返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n太爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n初初轉嗰陣用咗一星期習慣<br />\n依家可以唔使睇MON都可以打晒中文，雖然嗰陣打速成都可以唔睇MON打字，不過一啲字都係唔記得咩位置 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b015fa65820a8621c519c301c41477ff330ca5","tid":222964,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"用速成好多年<br />\n返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"48a5b9d9fa329556c735ee5b08ec8ccbcfc3f49b","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dfd9b017c733ec32f19795a5c81375267fa2a1","tid":222964,"uid":89743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:13:35.000Z","msg":"用Apple先最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n按竹已經有得揀「我」<br />\n唔知Windows有冇"},{"pid":"38d43eb231b9ec7060e087b5f624acf3d426478a","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用Apple先最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n按竹已經有得揀「我」<br />\n唔知Windows有冇</blockquote><br />\napple唔係輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc912d30af42b2ed9c077e58acf32c1ad786807","tid":222964,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"如果m$內置九方 玩完啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12a9d9d07a1609e9bd528ec6e0c83a0dfbfec70","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果m$內置九方 玩完啦你</blockquote><br />\n世界沒有如果"},{"pid":"e0b2afb6c88ddc744bacf02841d25f773166d970","tid":222964,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"用倉頡當然用Google廣東話輸入法"},{"pid":"efe59271e584c60f350d10c4b8903cef28bfbb73","tid":222964,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"以前學倉頡速成，覺得好難記<br />\n後尾google出左拼音就用到宜家<br />\n我覺得用英文鍵盤打倉頡碼好唔logical<br />\n同埋要轉英文好麻煩"},{"pid":"6131c9789d7d566316c9e06d87d86e1336d1645b","tid":222964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前學倉頡速成，覺得好難記<br />\n後尾google出左拼音就用到宜家<br />\n我覺得用英文鍵盤打倉頡碼好唔logical<br />\n同埋要轉英文好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n蝗拼定粵拼？"},{"pid":"454fd07cb17ba4378cc75c1098cf74d161b90688","tid":222964,"uid":113465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"電腦點先可以用倉頡一路打的碼一路出字<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hngeitdq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhngeitdq&h=407a536f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁樣"},{"pid":"6d72c0ac4aa7c969c18816034b5c62b65bc59ce3","tid":222964,"uid":84507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"倉頡本身拆碼唔係難，只要記哂變形就自己拼到，根本唔洗記碼<br />\n要背碼本身個學習方法都錯誤啦<br />\n打左十幾年倉頡到而家人地問我點打我都係順序拆返出來，唔拆根本就唔記得LOL<br />\n邊個再話學倉頡要背碼真係死全家<br />\n而家科技發達唔係比你查字典呀<br />\n係你手機電腦都好，打兩個碼已經出到個字比你揀<br />\n根本唔洗打哂<br />\n而且唔會因為同音搞到錯字，唔會比人自動改正......<br />\n呢D 先係打倉頡既優點"},{"pid":"f9a549d9473f2fa8b8e5a305108ba9852591062c","tid":222964,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T21:39:27.000Z","msg":"而家科技咁發達應該用語音輸入法<br />\n依家語音輸入法又快又準，不過排版都係要靠鍵盤"},{"pid":"3bbd53f073c7fc8585cea5395d58f3f675515e19","tid":222964,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"以前用九方同手寫, 之後俾老母逼學倉頡, 方便咗好多, 不過打字好多時要望住keyboard(中英都係)"},{"pid":"2af9033f82fa859d1ffeb725434280087e1eb733","tid":222964,"uid":107064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T04:18:19.000Z","msg":"拼音here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打詞語同句子好撚快"}]}